message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with signal processing and audio source separation. Other likely categories could be cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper uses deep learning techniques, cs.CV (computer vision) as the proposed method can be extended to image segmentation, cs.SI (social and information networks) as the method involves clustering, and cs.SY (systems and control) as the method can be extended to microphone array methods.
